Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.50,0:01:12.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I won't be a moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.30,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Hanna.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.72,0:01:17.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Princess.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.97,0:01:18.97,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Anne?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.30,0:01:21.68,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.64,0:01:23.68,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.02,0:01:25.18,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.10,0:01:27.60,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.60,0:01:28.81,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.90,0:01:38.66,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You never let {\i1}me{\i0} into your room,\N even though I've asked you so many times!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.66,0:01:40.07,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.07,0:01:41.53,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking to you, Hanna!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.79,0:01:44.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be rude, Anne.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.29,0:01:45.41,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to snap at her.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.10,0:02:07.23,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, what's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.23,0:02:09.10,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hanna.{hi hanna}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.44,0:02:12.27,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Are you two {\i1}still{\i0} fighting?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.27,0:02:13.69,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.36,0:02:22.08,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Grea, I've called the repairman.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.08,0:02:24.99,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Shall we head up and wait together?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.91,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.25,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?{lmao}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.88,0:02:40.30,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, um... Uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.81,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Hanna.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.81,0:02:46.43,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.40,0:03:00.36,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! This is all wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.79,0:03:12.04,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Pitty pat pat, build the snowman just like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.04,0:03:13.21,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Pitty pat pat—{Lou is a national treasure.}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.84,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Okay everyone, open up your textbooks.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.84,0:03:21.68,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Today we'll be talking about how \Nhealing magic can help clear your mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.14,0:03:28.73,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Holy magic is well known for its effects on the body.\N Take exorcism and strengthening spells, for example.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.73,0:03:30.60,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Now turn to the next page.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.35,0:03:36.94,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,In fact, experiments in holy magic \Nfrom ancient times have demonstrated
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.94,0:03:41.57,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,that it can have tremendous \Neffects on the mind as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.03,0:03:48.12,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}So not only can it be used to heal your body,\N it can also to help you overcome negative emotions.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.12,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,In practice, spirits need to be—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.12,GJM_Overlap,,0,0,0,,Anne...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.87,0:03:56.88,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Er, spirits need to be convinced\N to lend their power—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.26,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's enough for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.84,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to revise.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.48,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What should we do after school?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.36,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Wanna go to that place again?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.36,0:04:18.86,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What place?{same}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.61,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That place we went last time.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.89,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Look, Anne, aren't those—{;_;}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.56,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,How did things end up like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.62,0:09:25.41,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Anne.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.63,0:09:30.46,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Were you playing the piano?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.21,0:09:32.88,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's so cold that...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.79,0:09:42.39,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,my hands went all numb.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.59,0:10:20.26,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Shall we go and have tea?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.27,0:10:27.94,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.46,0:11:44.97,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Once, two opposing, chaotic powers \Nengulfed the world in the flames of battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.55,0:11:47.72,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This land{once again} became a battlefield.{I have a feeling また doesn't have to mean "again" and can have some other meaning in this context because it seems kind of weird here}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.14,0:11:53.73,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The people that fell to pain \Nand sorrow raised a prayer to God.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.52,0:11:58.51,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It was then that Seraph Manaria \Nwas sent from the heavens
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.51,0:12:01.61,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,to quell the flames of battle that ravaged the lands.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.40,0:12:06.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But we now face a crisis \Nthat threatens that very peace.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.33,0:12:11.62,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I—no, all of us—must face it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.00,0:12:16.38,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You may not be aware of how dire the situation is,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.38,0:12:23.30,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}but even the most trivial of disagreements can form\N a vicious cycle of confrontation and hatred.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.30,0:12:26.89,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Two chaotic powers are about \Nto rise from our very academy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.43,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,By "two chaotic powers," do you mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.68,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,...the Princess and Grea?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.18,0:12:36.31,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If these powers collide, an endless battle will ensue.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.31,0:12:39.19,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Not only will it affect the academy,\N the entire world will be plunged into chaos!{I wanna write this better but I don't wanna use a semicolon, send help}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.53,0:12:43.57,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,All will be led down a path of grief and sorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.90,0:12:47.83,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Are you saying this could spark war\N between the two kingdoms?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.28,0:12:51.91,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,To turn a blind eye to this problem \Nwould be to disgrace our ancestors,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.91,0:12:56.17,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,who prayed for and protected the peace of this land.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.17,0:13:00.82,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}So those of us who love Manaria and came \Nhere to gather the fruit of her knowledge
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.82,0:13:03.47,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,must stand together to protect her peace!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.02,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Allow me to take this vow!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.43,0:13:13.14,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}As student council president, I will stand firm against\N these powers' chaos to avoid this terrible fate!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.14,0:13:16.40,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I pray you'll give me your blessing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.81,GJM_Overlap,,0,0,0,,President...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.40,GJM_Overlap,,0,0,0,,Hanna!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,She's so dazzling!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.90,0:13:24.19,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I will now head out to battle, \Nto protect the peace of our academy!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.19,0:13:26.32,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.99,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll fight with you too!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.53,GJM_Overlap,,0,0,0,,I'll come with you as well!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.78,0:13:29.12,GJM_Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Me too!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.12,0:13:29.78,GJM_Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.24,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.21,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Princess, Grea!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.21,0:13:48.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please spare a moment to listen\N to what we... have to... say?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.05,0:13:49.39,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This really warms you up!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.51,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's very relaxing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.64,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hanna?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.35,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What's everyone doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.56,GJM_Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}By the way, where did you buy these tea leaves?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.77,0:14:03.36,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Have they made up?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.57,GJM_Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's a store in town I'm really fond of.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.53,GJM_Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We should go together some time!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.99,0:14:06.99,GJM_Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, that sounds great.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.99,0:14:10.82,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,How can you two worry everyone like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.82,0:14:13.87,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,My determination was all for naught!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.34,0:14:34.89,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Manaria Friends, Episode 10:\NTheir Promise.
